Symbol outline of a single Rust file

Usage: cs topology outline [OPTIONS] <FILE>

Arguments:
  <FILE>  Path to the `.rs` file

Options:
      --config <PATH>  Path to configuration file
  -v, --verbose        Enable verbose output
      --json           Output in JSON format
  -h, --help           Print help
